Sentencas: The crystal structure and charge density of (Ba0.5Sr0.5)(CO0.8Fe0.2)O-2.33, a promising cathode material for solid oxide fuel cells with lower operating temperatures, were investigated by the Rietveld refinement method and the maximum entropy method (MEM) using neutron and synchrotron X-ray diffraction data.
Titulo: Determination of the crystal structure and charge density of (Ba0.5Sr0.5)(Co0.8Fe0.2)O2.33 by Rietveld refinement and maximum entropy method analysis

Sentencas: The crystal structure of (Ba0.5Sr0.5)(Co0.8Fe0.2)O-2.33 was refined by using the orthorhombic Prima space group and the split atom model to cation sites.
Titulo: Determination of the crystal structure and charge density of (Ba0.5Sr0.5)(Co0.8Fe0.2)O2.33 by Rietveld refinement and maximum entropy method analysis

Sentencas: The occupancy of 01 (4c) and 02 (8d) sites are 0.59 and 0.87, respectively.
Titulo: Determination of the crystal structure and charge density of (Ba0.5Sr0.5)(Co0.8Fe0.2)O2.33 by Rietveld refinement and maximum entropy method analysis

Sentencas: From the MEM analysis, we found that (Ba0.5Sr0.5)(Co0.8Fe0.2)O-2.33 possessed both covalent and ionic bonds.
Titulo: Determination of the crystal structure and charge density of (Ba0.5Sr0.5)(Co0.8Fe0.2)O2.33 by Rietveld refinement and maximum entropy method analysis
